## Overriding `List.add` ##

Note that overriding [`List.add`](http://download.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/List.html#add%28E%29) (or [`List.addAll`](http://download.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/List.html#addAll%28java.util.Collection%29) for that matter) to insert elements in a sorted fashion would be a **direct violation of the interface specification**.

